reserve_tb -> reserve_tb_all
left_join(reserve_tb_all, reserve_tb %>%
  group_by(hotel_id) %>%
  summarise(res_cnt = n()) %>%
  mutate(rsv_rank=min_rank(desc(res_cnt))), by = c("hotel_id") )
